Package: snaputils
Version: 0.2.6
Title: SNAP-Specific Utilities for Shiny Apps
Description: Common utility functions, settings and references used across multiple Shiny apps
    specific to a SNAP context. This package inherents from the apputils package and is a 
    satellite member of the SNAPverse collection of R packages.
Author: Matthew Leonawicz [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Matthew Leonawicz <mfleonawicz@alaska.edu>
